IMAPAccount gmail-home-account
Host imap.gmail.com
User dave@waveform.org.uk
PassCmd "/usr/bin/gpg -q -d --no-tty --for-your-eyes-only $XDG_RUNTIME_DIR/isync-home 2>/dev/null"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2

IMAPAccount gmail-work-account
Host imap.gmail.com
User dave.jones@canonical.com
PassCmd "/usr/bin/gpg -q -d --no-tty --for-your-eyes-only $XDG_RUNTIME_DIR/isync-work 2>/dev/null"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2

IMAPStore gmail-home
Account gmail-home-account

MaildirStore local-home
Flatten .
Path ~/.mail/home/
Inbox ~/.mail/home/INBOX

IMAPStore gmail-work
Account gmail-work-account

MaildirStore local-work
Flatten .
Path ~/.mail/work/
Inbox ~/.mail/work/INBOX

# Global defaults
Create Both
Remove Both
SyncState *

Channel home
Master :gmail-home:
Slave :local-home:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Drafts" "[Gmail]/Spam" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/Trash"

Channel work
Master :gmail-work:
Slave :local-work:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Drafts" "[Gmail]/Spam" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/Trash"
